reviews.review_text: nugget Lawdy, lawdy.  Thank you Pearson, thank you Healy, thank you Miller.  Thank you dancer, thank you prancer, thank you fancier than thou.  Serious tip?  Late-80s Dead at its near-best, and phenomenal sound qual.  Meadows was the place to be, and this one will be in the soon-to-be-released Points of Light, 100 Top Shows of the Brent Era.  God bless all of you, especially if you were there.
